text:
🍂🌿Beautifully landscaped Bioswales at Tampines Boulevard Park East.
💨🌧️Bioswales are used to manage rainwater.
⛲🌩️It functions to slow down and filter out rainwater runoff pollutants before they are discharged into open drains.
🏔️🗻It also encourages infiltration, by allowing rainwater to seep into the ground thereby replenishing the groundwater.
🍁🍀Besides, Bioswales naturally beautifies the surrounding overall landscape and enrich biodiversity.
